dct_description_sm: Basically black and white but with parks indicated in blue, city transportation lines in blue, highways in broad red lines, city limits in dashed red lines. Includes Street Index and listing of public buildings, colleges, schools, hospitals, transportation, industrial sites. Reverse includes photos, information, Facts, Historical Facts, and Development.
Imprint: Fort Wayne, Indiana: Shockney & Kain. 1946.
Dimensions: 65 x 55 cm, on sheet 67 x 56 cm; Scale: Scale not given.
